author: jleroux
msg: * Canada GeoId for Province prefixed with CA- as it should be (following ISO 3166-2:CA,  http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_3166-2:CA)

* USA GeoId for Province prefixed with US- as it should be (following ISO 3166-2:US,  http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_3166-2:US). I did not see any reasons to no use the same scheme for "US Armed Forces provinces"
No other countries had the same problem
